<h2>chaos.social</h2>
<p>chaos.social - because anarchy is much more fun with friends.<br>
chaos.social is a <em>small</em> Mastodon instance for and by the chaos community. We provide a small community space - <em>be excellent to each other</em> (and read the <a href="https://chaos.social/about/more/">rules</a> if you're not sure what that means).<br>
Follow @ordnung for low-traffic instance-related updates.</p>
